'''''The Perfect Picture''''' ni [[Gana|firime yo muri Gana]] yakozwe kandi yanditswe na Shirley Frimpong-Manso mu 2009<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film849708.html</ref><ref>https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/537334833</ref>.  

== Umugambi ==
Mubintu bisa nkubuzima butunganye, abagore batatu beza bagiye kuzuza imyaka mirongo itatu<ref>https://www.africancelebs.com/perfect-picture-movie-sparrow-productions/</ref>,bagerageza bashize amanga kugirango bahindure ubuzima bwabo nubwo ibizazane bitabura<ref>https://www.bellanaija.com/2019/12/ghanaian-movie-the-perfect-picture-ten-years-later-premiered-with-the-leading-ladies-in-attendance/</ref><ref>https://stories.showmax.com/the-best-of-shirley-frimpong-on-showmax/</ref>. Hamwe nubukwe busa nkaho bugiye kurimbuka kuva mbere, kugeza kumukandida udashoboka no gukurikirana urukundo rutagira iherezo<ref>https://nollywoodpost.com/post/the-perfect-picture-ten-years-later-a-cliche</ref>, inshuti eshatu ziziga amasomo akomeye yubuzima, imbogamizi zubukwe<ref>https://www.pulse.com.gh/entertainment/movies/shirley-frimpong-manso-announces-the-perfect-picture-sequel-after-a-decade/w5xt0fk</ref><ref>https://nigeriacelebrities.com/shirley-frimpong-mansos-the-perfect-picture-10-years-later-premieres-on-netflix-in-july/</ref>, impfu zo gukundana nibihembo bya guseka neza mu gihu cy'akababaro<ref>https://baseafricatv.net/shirley-frimpong-manso-fails-to-credit-senyo-foli-in-her-movie-perfect-picture/</ref>. Ishusho Yuzuye itanga ubushishozi bwamabara kandi asetsa mwisi aho ibintu byose bitunganye nkubuzima bwawe ninshuti zawe<ref>https://www.nigeriafilms.com/movie-news/85-film-tv-workshop/5108-shirley-manso-s-perfect-picture-a-perfect-disappointment</ref><ref>https://www.telerama.fr/cinema/films/the-perfect-picture-ten-years-later,n6666136.php</ref>.

